OL,3,CCold weather payments: Could you be
OL,4,Centitled to them?
OL,6,FThe UK has faced persistent cold
OL,7,Fweather, along with its first named
OL,8,Fstorm of 2026, Storm Goretti, which
OL,9,Fbrought snow and freezing conditions.
OL,11,FMany households have had to turn up
OL,12,Fthe heating, pushing up energy bills.
OL,14,FBut for those struggling to pay, you
OL,15,Fmay be eligible for government support
OL,16,Fthrough cold weather payments.
OL,18,FWhat are cold-weather payments?
