OL,3,CCold weather payments: Could you be
OL,4,Centitled to them?
OL,6,FThe government provides #25 payments
OL,7,Fto people on specific benefits in
OL,8,Fareas where the average temperature is
OL,9,Frecorded as zero degrees or lower for
OL,10,Fseven consecutive days.
OL,12,FPeople can receive a #25 payment for
OL,13,Feach period of seven days that records
OL,14,Fthese temperatures.
OL,16,FPayments are made per household and
OL,17,Fnot per person, so only one payment
OL,18,Fwill be made even if multiple people
OL,19,Fin the same household qualify.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
