OL,3,CCold weather payments: Could you be
OL,4,Centitled to them?
OL,6,FThose receiving Universal Credit must
OL,7,Falso not be employed or 'gainfully
OL,8,Fself-employed', or have a partner who
OL,9,Fis either. Either the claimant or
OL,10,Ftheir partner must also have a health
OL,11,Fcondition or disability and have
OL,12,Flimited capability for work, or have a
OL,13,Fchild under five living with them.
OL,15,FThose who have a disabled child amount
OL,16,Fin their claim will also be eligible,
OL,17,Fregardless of whether the claimant or
OL,18,Ftheir partner is employed, self-
OL,19,Femployed or not working.
