OL,3,CCold weather payments: Could you be
OL,4,Centitled to them?
OL,6,FThose in receipt of support for
OL,7,Fmortgage interest are eligible if one
OL,8,Fof the following applies: A severe or
OL,9,Fenhanced disability premium, a
OL,10,Fpensioner premium, a child who is
OL,11,Fdisabled, or a child under 5 living
OL,12,Fwith the claimant.
OL,14,FYou can check whether your postcode is
OL,15,Feligible to receive a cold weather
OL,16,Fpayment and, if so, how many by typing
OL,17,Fin your postcode here.
OL,19,FThose in Scotland are not eligible to
OL,20,Freceive cold weather payments.
