OL,3,CCold weather payments: Could you be
OL,4,Centitled to them?
OL,6,FAfter each period of very cold weather
OL,7,Fin your area, you should get a payment
OL,8,Fwithin 14 working days. It's paid into
OL,9,Fthe same bank or building society
OL,10,Faccount as your benefit payments.
OL,12,FIf you do not get your cold-weather
OL,13,Fpayments and believe you are eligible,
OL,14,Ftell the Pension Service or Jobcentre
OL,15,FPlus.
OL,17,FIf you're getting Universal Credit,
OL,18,Fsign in to your account and add a note
OL,19,Fto your journal.
